query:
SELECT 
  dr.id,
  dr.date,
  b.name as branch_name,
  dr.cashAmount,
  dr.networkAmount,
  dr.total,
  dr.isMatched
FROM daily_revenues dr
LEFT JOIN branches b ON dr.branchId = b.id
ORDER BY dr.date DESC
LIMIT 10;
